com.palomamobile.android.sdk.core

Interface IServiceManager<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAuthManager, IFriendManager, IMediaManager, IMessageManager, IMessageThreadManager, INotificationManager, IUserManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MessageThreadManager

    public interface IServiceManager<T>
    Defines a ServiceManager implementation in terms of the API service it manages. IServiceSupport provides access to the various IServiceManager implementations via the IServiceSupport.getServiceManager(Class) and IServiceSupport.registerServiceManager(Class, IServiceManager) methods.
